      ],
      "source": "https://ci.carmel.ca.us/local-history"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "By 1913, the Arts and Crafts Club began teaching aspiring painters, actors, and craftsmen, nurturing Carmel’s artistic legacy.",
